title: Phase 2. Parameters of Barter / Trading System
body:
Phase 1 of the Barter / Trading System has passed on Snapshot/DAO as of Sept 13th, 2021. 
Next step is the parameters and details of it. **If this were to pass, we would bring it to Phase 3 and vote on any remaining factors** This is a Single Choice vote so choose wisely. I am proposing that we;

(ALL OPTIONS INCLUDE THAT; The person making the offer can set a time in which the offer expires and have the ability to cancel the offer whenever one wants.

1. Impose a fee of 0.1 GHST for someone to propose a trade whether or not the recipient agrees or not. THIS FEE WILL BE BURNED.

2. Impose a fee of 0.1 GHST for someone to propose a trade whether or not the recipient agrees or not. 0.1 GHST goes to the TREASURY.

3. Impose a fee of 0.1 GHST for someone to propose a trade whether or not the recipient agrees or not. 0.05 GHST to go to TREASURY and 0.05 GHST to be BURNED.

4. Impose a fee of 0.1 GHST for someone to propose a trade whether or not the recipient agrees or not. 0.05 GHST to the TREASURY and 0.05 GHST for RARITY FARMING.

5. Impose a fee of 0.2 GHST for someone to propose a trade whether or not the recipient agrees or not. 0.1 GHST goes to Rarity Farming and 0.1 GHST will go to Treasury.

6. Impose a fee of 0.2 GHST for someone to propose a trade whether or not the recipient agrees or not. 0.1 GHST goes to the Treasury and 0.1 GHST will be BURNED.

7. Impose a fee of 0.2 GHST for someone to propose a trade whether or not the recipient agrees or not. 0.1 GHST goes to the Rarity Farming and 0.1 GHST will be BURNED.

8. NO!! Needs to be revised!! Redo Phase 2 Vote on another date!!
